RULESET: UI TOKEN MIGRATION v1.0

Purpose:
Ensure all UI elements in the codebase migrate from legacy Tailwind utility styling and inline colors to the new design tokens defined in `packages/design-system/tokens/design-tokens.ts`.

‚ö†Ô∏è Rules apply ONLY to files inside: `apps/web/**` ‚Äî never modify files in `packages/design-system/**`.

-----------------------------------

üé® COLOR RULES
- Replace all hex values (#xxxxxx) with the closest match from: tokens.colors.*
- Replace Tailwind color classes (e.g., `text-gray-500`, `bg-blue-500`) with tokens-based CSS variables.
- If token mapping is unclear, comment: // TODO: TokenMapNeeded(color)

-----------------------------------

üî† TYPOGRAPHY RULES
- Replace Tailwind sizing classes (`text-xs`, `text-sm`, `text-xl`) with token equivalents.
- Inline font-size declarations must be replaced with: style={{ fontSize: tokens.font.size.* }}

-----------------------------------

üì¶ SPACING & RADIUS
- Replace all custom radius (`rounded-[x]`) with tokens.radius.*
- Replace spacing like `p-3`, `m-4` only when used stylistically, not layout-critical.

-----------------------------------

‚öõÔ∏è COMPONENT MIGRATION
- Replace HTML <button> with `<Button />`
- Replace custom progress bars with `@repo/design-system/components/ProgressBar`
- Replace inline alerts with new `<Alert />` component (if unavailable, comment: TODO: Create Alert component)

-----------------------------------

üß™ SAFETY + OUTPUT
- After each file transformation, output:
  - Summary of replacements
  - Unresolved TODO tokens
  - Whether file is considered: Fully migrated | Partially migrated | Needs manual review

---

üé® STYLE SYSTEM: "Hybrid Fitness Premium (Mode D)" ‚Äî PERMANENT RULE

Apply automatically to all UI components and refactors:

1. VISUAL LANGUAGE
   - Minimal, clean, light spacing, no heavy borders
   - Subtle shadows only for interactive elements (cards, sheets, floating UI)
   - Primary color ONLY for: CTAs, progress, active nav, success confirmations

2. TYPOGRAPHY
   - Headings: clean, bold but not oversized
   - Body: neutral, softer tone using textMuted token
   - No decorative/playful fonts

3. RADIUS SYSTEM
   - Buttons: tokens.radius.md
   - Cards & modals: tokens.radius.lg
   - Icons & inputs: tokens.radius.sm
   - tokens.radius.full ONLY for avatars/circular UI

4. INTERACTION & MOTION
   - Micro-interactions: scale(0.98) on press, soft transitions
   - Page transitions: smooth and subtle, no hard slides
   - Progress/health: slight motion for feedback OK

5. COLOR PHILOSOPHY
   - Layout: neutral grayscale with subtle contrast
   - Brand color: intentional meaning, not decoration

6. DARK MODE
   - No aggressive color inversion
   - Soft layered surfaces, textMuted softened, primary consistent

